<mj-section background-color="__brandSurface__" padding="16px 24px 20px" border="2px solid __brandBorder__" border-top="0">
  <mj-column>
    <mj-divider border-color="__brandBorder__" border-width="2px" padding="0 0 12px" />
    <mj-text
      align="left"
      font-size="12px"
      color="__brandMuted__"
      line-height="18px"
      font-family="'Courier New', Courier, 'Lucida Console', monospace"
      padding="0"
    >
      此邮件由 __productName__ 自动发送，请勿直接回复。<br />
      如有疑问请联系 <a href="mailto:__supportEmail__" style="color:__brandPrimary__;text-decoration:underline;font-weight:700;">__supportEmail__</a>
    </mj-text>
    <mj-text
      align="left"
      font-size="11px"
      color="__brandMuted__"
      font-family="'Courier New', Courier, 'Lucida Console', monospace"
      padding="10px 0 0"
    >
      © __year__ __productName__ · <a href="__frontendBaseUrl__" style="color:__brandMuted__;text-decoration:underline;">__frontendBaseUrl__</a>
    </mj-text>
  </mj-column>
</mj-section>
